    <exercise xml:id="auto_yetd6oft">
      <statement>
        <p xml:id="auto_x66l7zet">
          <m>A(0,4)\, B(-3,0) \text{ and } C(0,2)</m> are the coordinates of <m>\Delta ABC.</m> Reflect the triangle over mirror line <m>x = 0.</m>
           Prove that the triangle and its image are congruent and state the test of congruence criterion. 
        </p>
