    <exercise xml:id="auto_h23fdoll">
      <statement>
        <p xml:id="auto_xuvobx53">
          Construct an equilateral triangle <m>UVW</m> with sides <m>6\,cm.\,X</m> is the midpoint of <m>UW</m> and <m>VX</m> is perpendicular to <m>UW.</m>
           Show that <m>\Delta UVX \, \cong \, \Delta VWX.</m> State the test of congruence criterion.
        </p>
      </statement>
      <answer>
        <p>
          By SAS (Side-Angle-Side) the triangles are congruent.
        </p>
      </answer>
